<template>
  <van-nav-bar :title="title" left-text left-arrow @click-left="onBack" />
</template>

<script>
import { NavBar } from 'vant';
export default {
  name: 'headerNav',
  components: {
    [NavBar.name]: NavBar,
  },
  props: {
    title: String,
  },
  methods: {
    onBack () {
      history.back();
    },
  }
}
</script>

<style>
</style>
